      <item>
        <title>No referral links policy</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[@Mopman Mopman]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/u/mopman">@Mopman</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>I’ve never really had much of a problem with referral links, when you think about it, they’re not evil or underhand at all - if you are getting paid to refer people to a site, and you post that link on the forum, you are indeed referring people to the site.</p>
<p>If the site has no relevance or interest to us then it is spam like any other, of course, but just because it is a referral link does not make it spam, in my opinion.</p>
          </blockquote>
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/t/no-referral-links-policy/144597/4">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
